[[File:文化大革命_新疆_袁昌熾_通緝令.jpg|右]]

{{expand|time=2017-09-28T07:17:11+00:00}}
'''反動學術權威'''是[[文化大革命|文化大革命]]爆發前夕及以後，[[中华人民共和国|中华人民共和国]]社会對部分高级[[知識份子|知識份子]]的蔑稱。

此称谓被认为起源于[[毛澤東|毛澤東]]语“[[知识越多越反动|知识越多越反动]]”<ref>{{Cite web|title=[转载]路线错了，知识越多越反动|url=http://blog.sciencenet.cn/blog-40692-1038399.html|accessdate=2019-11-01|author=张成岗|date=|format=|work=|publisher=科学网|language=|archive-date=2019-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191101182154/http://blog.sciencenet.cn/blog-40692-1038399.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=蔡长运：孔子论“知识越多越反动！” - 学者观点|url=http://www.szhgh.com/Article/opinion/xuezhe/2019-02-24/193388.html|accessdate=2019-11-01|author=|date=|format=|work=|publisher=红歌会网|language=|archive-date=2019-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191101182156/http://www.szhgh.com/Article/opinion/xuezhe/2019-02-24/193388.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，很多知识分子因此被[[下放|下放]][[五七幹校|五七幹校]]或[[上山下鄉運動|插隊]]落戶。亦有知识分子如[[熊十力|熊十力]]、[[田漢|田漢]]、[[老舍|老舍]]、[[翦伯贊|翦伯贊]]、[[傅雷|傅雷]]等，因被视为反动学术权威而[[自杀|自杀]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=文革时期国学大师熊十力痛苦悲吟：中国文化亡了|url=http://news.ifeng.com/history/minjianshuoshi/zhouwei/detail_2012_03/18/13273000_0.shtml|accessdate=2019-10-26|author=|date=|format=|work=|publisher=凤凰网|language=|archive-date=2019-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191026035534/http://news.ifeng.com/history/minjianshuoshi/zhouwei/detail_2012_03/18/13273000_0.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=国歌词作者文革中被逼死：生前被迫喝下自己小便|url=http://news.ifeng.com/history/phtv/wdzgx/detail_2012_01/13/11956110_5.shtml|accessdate=2019-10-26|author=|date=|format=|work=|publisher=凤凰网|language=|archive-date=2019-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191026035532/http://news.ifeng.com/history/phtv/wdzgx/detail_2012_01/13/11956110_5.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=老舍为什么投太平湖自杀？|url=http://www.sohu.com/a/285405184_120078003|accessdate=2019-10-26|author=肖军|date=|format=|work=|publisher=搜狐|language=en|archive-date=2019-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191026035531/http://www.sohu.com/a/285405184_120078003|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=翦伯赞自杀之谜|url=http://www.aisixiang.com/data/3956.html|accessdate=2019-10-26|author=|date=|format=|work=|publisher=爱思想|language=|archive-date=2019-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191026035532/http://www.aisixiang.com/data/3956.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=1966年，傅雷夫妇自杀，三个人的命运随之改变|url=http://www.sohu.com/a/244104534_220095|accessdate=2019-11-01|author=|date=|format=|work=|publisher=搜狐|language=en|archive-date=2019-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191101083229/http://www.sohu.com/a/244104534_220095|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=最后的傅雷|url=http://book.ifeng.com/a/20150902/17268_1.shtml|accessdate=2019-11-01|author=|date=|format=|work=|publisher=凤凰网|language=|archive-date=2019-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191101182406/http://book.ifeng.com/a/20150902/17268_1.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

